cts. ";This raw, haunting, richly poetic, deeply emotional play affected me as no other entry did.";  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aBrothers and sistersvDrama. 0aFamily secretsvDrama. 0aViolent crimesvDrama. 7aDRAMA / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z97831105379940 cprintz978030018485340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030018604840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300186048423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300186048/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY